data.description: Welcome to 103 Estero Court! With 1,831 square feet of living space, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom boasts an open floor plan that is perfect for effortless entertaining.  Four generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for you to relax and recharge. The master suite is a true retreat, complete with a private en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. BRAND NEW ROOF and NEW CARPETING just installed.  Priced to sell.  This home being sold as is. Seller will make no additional repairs. MOTIVATED SELLER!
